        "775": {
          "vnum": 775,
          "name": "Marshy Water",
          "description": "The banks spread here allowing clean natural light to illuminate brown grainy water, swirling thickly in aimless eddies. A broad muddy slope emerges from a break in the forest to the south where there seem to be signs of recent activity.",
