        "584": {
          "vnum": 584,
          "name": "North Bank of the River",
          "description": "The cobblestones end here at a wooden bridge which spans the river spilling into Decaren Bay just to the east. It looks as it was made to support heavy loads judging by the thick support beams spanning its length. Approaching the river bank, the ground becomes muddy and the grass thick, and mosquitos buzz around your head annoyingly.",
