        "588": {
          "vnum": 588,
          "name": "Bridge Over the River Frektal",
          "description": "A pair of grooves run the length of the bridge. You assume these are to guide the heavily laden carts which seem to pass this way. Turning to the west, you can see several hundred feet down the river; a small plaque on the railing tells its name is Frektal. Odd looking barges, very flat and protruding a few inches from the water, float lazily by twenty feet below.",
