        "589": {
          "vnum": 589,
          "name": "South Bank of the River",
          "description": "You stand at the edge of the heavily foliated riverside. The air becomes sticky and hot and the presence of a wealth of life is immediately apparent as you slap at insects. A heavily used and wheel-rutted trail leads directly into the thick deciduous forest to the southwest.",
