        "590": {
          "vnum": 590,
          "name": "Through the Forest",
          "description": "A swath has been cut through the undergrowth allowing for easy travel. A canopy of exceedingly leafy branches arches over you, growing dramatically from massive sinewy trunks flanking the wide trail. A multitude of birds and insects fill the steamy air with their chirps and calls as you wipe the sweat from your brow and continue on your way.",
