        "591": {
          "vnum": 591,
          "name": "Approaching a Plantation",
          "description": "The dense greenery comes to an abrupt halt ahead at the corner of a what appears to be an expansive plantation. A soft breeze reaches you through the arching branches, relieving you from the moist oppressive heat. Breathing deeply, you take a moment to stop, look about, and cough uncontrollably. Good god, what is that smell?!",
