        "592": {
          "vnum": 592,
          "name": "In the Field",
          "description": "A field of several acres has been carved into the forest, walls of greenery rising all about its edges. Great water-filled paddies striate the land, densely occupied by a low-lying crop with exceedingly large orange-tipped leaves. By now, you've firmly clasped your shirt over your mouth and nose in a desperate and futile attempt to avoid their smell. The path continues to the west toward a small white structure on the field's far side. A pesky kierd harasses you. (6) Well aimed! You strike a pesky kierd dead! (67) A pesky kierd issues a bloodcurdling cry of pain!",
