          "name": "Corner of the Field",
          "description": "The field comes to a sharp corner here, a crude stone statue at its vertex. The statue is a faithful rendering of a half-elven woman, gazing out over the field benevolently, hands on her hips. The surface of the stone is rough indicating great age and doesn't look like any material you've seen in J'rel.",
