        "595": {
          "vnum": 595,
          "name": "Approaching a Farmhouse",
          "description": "Facing eastward across the field stands an odd white farmhouse. Two stories with a roof that curves out and down to the ground, the house differs from other J'relian architecture. A worn path leads around the house to its rear. A path along the northern edge of the field leads eastward away from the house before plunging into the forest on the other side.",
