        "596": {
          "vnum": 596,
          "name": "A Most Embarassing Bedroom",
          "description": "And this would be the room the Missus decorated. Virtually nothing besides the walls (a mural of lambs in the pasture) doesn't involve pink frills or white lace. An extensive collection of dolls sits on a white gold-gilded dresser next to a pair of small portraits of chubby-cheeked girls.",
