          "name": "Behind a Farmhouse",
          "description": "Despite the area cleared for the house, a small animal pen and toolshed, the sky remains obscured by overhanging branches. A sturdy plow sits next to an unusual wheeled piece of equipment. A nearby wagon is crop-stained and strong smelling. Tracks run both past the house to the east and down a narrow forest path you now notice to the west.",
