        "601": {
          "vnum": 601,
          "name": "Landing on the Frektal",
          "description": "A clearing has been hollowed out here, a natural dome created overhead by the tallest of trees. Wagon ruts lead from paths to the east, west and south toward a muddy landing that descends to the north into the river you can now see flowing slowly by. Rope-worn wooden moorings with quaintly decorated bronze caps line the bank and trampled poonk leaves lie strewn about.",
