        "603": {
          "vnum": 603,
          "name": "A Ragged Path",
          "description": "Trees and undergrowth push in around you, even moreso than the other similar wagon trails, and your clothing becomes damp with the moisture of greenery brushing by. Despite the presence of the same wheel ruts, foliage pushes up between them and it looks as if it would be with some small difficulty that a wagonload of poonk could be pulled through here.",
