        "604": {
          "vnum": 604,
          "name": "A Ragged Path",
          "description": "Light from neither sun nor moon penetrates the tangle of branches and broad leaves hanging over and around you. The chittering of animals and calls of birds become more insistent as do the insects searching for flesh. The wagon ruts come to an unnaturally abrupt end at an imposing curtain of leafy vines that block both your travel and sight.",
          "grid_x": -6,
          "grid_y": 1,
          "exits": {
