          "name": "An Unkempt Poonk Field",
          "description": "You stand at the northeast corner of a leafy field not unlike others, but with a noticeable lack of upkeep. Ferny undergrowth has begun to invade and mingle with the orange-tipped crop which looks overdue for harvest and trees have begun to shade the edges of the field.",
