          "name": "An Unkempt Poonk Field",
          "description": "Your feet slosh in your footwear as you make it to the field's northwestern extent. Small slimy creatures jerk about in the overgrown paddies, seemingly deeper here, and you desperately hope to not find any of them attached to you later. Through tears of stench-induced sickness, you think you can make out a small house to the south.",
