        "607": {
          "vnum": 607,
          "name": "At a Secluded Farmhouse",
          "description": "The forest doesn't seem to have been cleared so much as wedged aside by another convex-roofed farmhouse here at the southern edge of the field. Passage around the house is impossible and the windows are all permanently boarded over. Barely visible behind greenery, what appears to be a bronze chimney protrudes from the roof at a slight angle and fails to smoke.",
